# Hina Arshad Warraich

Hina Arshad Warraich () is a Pakistani politician and Member of the Provincial Assembly of the Punjab since 12 June 2025. She is the daughter of Former MPA Chaudhry Arshad Javaid Warraich.
Political career
She contested by-elections held on June 1, 2025 from constituency PP-52 Sialkot-IX, She defeated PTI candidate Fakhir Nishat Ghumman. She secured 78,702 votes, whereas Fakhir Nishat Ghumman obtained 40,037 votes.
